code: function complexNumberMultiply(num1, num2) { const parse = (str) => { const [real, imag] = str.split('+'); return [parseInt(real), parseInt(imag.slice(0, -1))]; }; const [a, b] = parse(num1); const [c, d] = parse(num2); const realPart = a * c - b * d; const imagPart = a * d + b * c; return `${realPart}+${imagPart}i`; }
